# 🧾 Inventory Search App

A full-stack inventory search application built using **React (Frontend)** and **Node.js + Express + Supabase (Backend)**.
Users can search products using filters like name, category, and price range.

---

## 🚀 Features

* 🔍 Search products by name
* 🗂️ Filter by category (grain, food, electronics)
* 💰 Filter by min and max price
* 📡 REST API integration
* ⚡ Real-time search results

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

### Frontend

* React.js
* JavaScript (ES6+)
* CSS

### Backend

* Node.js
* Express.js
* Supabase (Database)

---

